spur-winged plover
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a self-introduced wading bird, Vanellus miles, having olive-brown and white plumage, yellow facial wattles, and a yellow claw-like projection on the shoulder of each wing.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
